{"tid":1938132,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"小心23條街站！ 撐23條恐怖分子對平民發動襲襲！","createTime":"2020-03-22T10:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T13:40:28.000Z","uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4200ce21fc5f9d3448e7af77041215a3042b85ba","tid":1938132,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:37:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2945179692234298/?vh=e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2945179692234298%2F%3Fvh%3De&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=768782e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2945179692234298/?vh=e</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【睇片】撐 23 條街站再爆打人事件　呂智恆、黃嘉浩附近擺街站遭圍毆<br />\n<br />\n報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3blPBrD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3blPBrD&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=a7564175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3blPBrD</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯近日呼籲政府就《基本法》23 條立法，並與香港政研會、新界關注大聯盟組成「23 同盟」在全港多區收集簽名。基督徒社工呂智恆、前北區動源成員黃嘉浩今日稱，在粉嶺遭多名支持 23 條立法街站的男子襲擊，二人身體多處受傷需要送院。<br />\n<br />\n在今日下午近 5 時，呂智恆透過 FB 直播，稱現場有襲擊事件，但當他上前拍攝時即被人出手阻止，直播在混亂間中斷。在十多分鐘後，呂智恆及黃嘉浩在另一段直播中展示傷勢，及後警方到場處理案件。<br />\n<br />\n（網上片段）"},{"pid":"125492c6e5a9093395f7cbc45f136084cb53b156","tid":1938132,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"我冇辦法再忍受到呢種沉默嘅鎮壓"},{"pid":"d5a10c51973a340cf866cc137c854353e54c8658","tid":1938132,"uid":220690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:03:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3c077d55b9f26b20108a753193226bf20c442858","tid":1938132,"uid":55441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d931498509d3140a2760cc8232ef66110e17bd1f","tid":1938132,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c077d55b9f26b20108a7531